node.text:
We’ve seen photos before of this view, from the loggia of  @villamonastero . Now, this video, from our wonderful friend @pinkines ,allows us to see what it’s like to be there. Be sure to view this in reels to get the best effect and be sure to watch until the end to see @hotelvillacipressi in the distance. 
Wishing everyone a great health and a great day!
